content: I attended a text team training on 7/31. I completed the google form and was onboarded. I had access to several text team channels within a couple of days from that date.  I did check in regularly for texting opportunities but they were always completed for the day.  I checked in this evening and no longer have access to all of the text team channels. I don’t know where or how to direct this question as it was removed from the text team welcome announcements channel. Appreciate any help.
Hi <@1012791863293513879> while you were "away" the text team revised their onboarding. Since you are a texter from a while back, I will connect you with <@1257444318222876712> to get this sorted.
Hi <@1012791863293513879> Thanks! I'll send you a folllow up Direct Message now in Discord. Let me know if you don't see it.
